data.name: textBox3.Text
data.value: Voltage sensor calibration: To calibrate your sensor, use a multimeter to measure the voltage coming out of your ESC's battery-elimination circuit (these are black and red wires in the three-wire cable that is powering your APM board). Then subtract 0.3v from that value and enter it in field #1 at left.
